<p class=MsoBodyText style='margin-top:0in;margin-right:.5in;margin-bottom:
0in;margin-left:.5in;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-indent:.5in'><span
style='font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt'>Exiled from Palestine, the
Jewish people remained faithful to it in all the countries of their dispersion,
never ceasing to pray and hope for their return and the restoration of their
