<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:0in;margin-right:.5in;margin-bottom:0in;
margin-left:.5in;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-indent:.5in;mso-layout-grid-align:
none;text-autospace:none'>Then Jesus declared, &quot;I who speak to you am
he.&quot; (John 4:19-26)</p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:0in;margin-right:.5in;margin-bottom:0in;
margin-left:.5in;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-indent:.5in;mso-layout-grid-align:
none;text-autospace:none'><![if !supportEmptyParas]>&nbsp;<![endif]><o:p></o:p></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='text-indent:.5in'>Jesus didn’t come to the Jewish
people?<span style="mso-spacerun: yes">  </span>Really?<span
style="mso-spacerun: yes">  </span>Then how are we to explain the comment made
by the Magi when they came to Herod:</p>

<p class=MsoNormal><![if !supportEmptyParas]>&nbsp;<![endif]><o:p></o:p></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:0in;margin-right:.5in;margin-bottom:0in;
margin-left:.5in;margin-bottom:.0001pt;mso-layout-grid-align:none;text-autospace:
none'>“Where is the one who has been born king of the Jews? We saw his star in
the east and have come to worship him.&quot; (Matthew 2:2)</p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='mso-layout-grid-align:none;text-autospace:none'><![if !supportEmptyParas]>&nbsp;<![endif]><o:p></o:p></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='text-indent:.5in;mso-layout-grid-align:none;
text-autospace:none'>And why did Jesus respond this way to Pilate:</p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='mso-layout-grid-align:none;text-autospace:none'><![if !supportEmptyParas]>&nbsp;<![endif]><o:p></o:p></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:0in;margin-right:.5in;margin-bottom:0in;
margin-left:.5in;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-indent:.5in;mso-layout-grid-align:
none;text-autospace:none'>Meanwhile Jesus stood before the governor, and the
governor asked him, &quot;Are you the king of the Jews?&quot; </p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:0in;margin-right:.5in;margin-bottom:0in;
margin-left:.5in;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-indent:.5in;mso-layout-grid-align:
none;text-autospace:none'>&quot;Yes, it is as you say,&quot; Jesus replied.
